{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"80c6b3a935","title":"在修改《林彪同志委托江青同志召开的部队文艺工作座谈会纪要》时所加的话","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"8b5757d33a","index":0,"year":1966,"month":3,"day":null,"articleId":"80c6b3a935","article":{}}],"tags":[{"name":"林彪","id":"44b4a39710","type":"人物"},{"name":"江青","id":"82305e518c","type":"人物"},{"name":"毛泽东","id":"dd2b275f6c","type":"人物"},{"name":"发言","id":"e23dcf99fa","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wansui5","name":"毛泽东思想万岁（1961-1968卷）（1968年武汉版）","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"未知","files":"/books/wansui5a.pdf","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"wansui5":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"bad1e34514","type":"title","text":"在修改《林彪同志委托江青同志召开的部队文艺工作座谈会纪要》时所加的话","index":0,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"80c6b3a935","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"9691e5c95e","type":"paragraph","text":"搞掉这条黑线之后，还会有将来的黑线，还得再斗争。所以，这是一场艰巨、复杂、长期的斗争，要经过几十年甚至几百年的努力。这是关系到我国革命前途的大事，也是关系到世界革命前途的大事。","index":1,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"80c6b3a935","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"609cd5adf6","type":"paragraph","text":"过去十几年的教训是：我们抓迟了。只抓过一些个别的问题，没有全盘的系统的抓起来，而只要我们不抓，很多阵地也就只好听任黑线去占领，这是一条严重的教训。","index":2,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"80c6b3a935","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"930da83720","type":"paragraph","text":"×××","index":3,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"80c6b3a935","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"a30ee8d792","type":"paragraph","text":"文艺上反对外国修正主义的斗争，不能只捉丘赫拉依之类小人物，要捉大的，捉肖洛霍夫，要敢于碰他。他是修正主义文艺的鼻祖。","index":4,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"80c6b3a935","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"9ede64c93e","type":"paragraph","text":"×××","index":5,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"80c6b3a935","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"3ba57a2920","type":"paragraph","text":"须知其他阶级的代表人物也是有他们的党性原则的，并且很顽强。","index":6,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"80c6b3a935","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":487,"end":487}}}},"__N_SSG":true}